# VEHICLE::SET_CARGOBOB_PICKUP_MAGNET_PULL_ROPE_LENGTH

## Summary
Set how much extra rope will be provided to allow the magnet to pull itself to the nearest entity

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** cargobob
* **FLOAT** magnetPullRopeLength
